lead_paragraph: Trent Boult is expected to be fit for New Zealand's opening one-day international against Australia in Sydney on Sunday after the strike bowler missed the second test win over Pakistan due to knee discomfort.

headline.print_headline: Boult Set to Return for ODI Opener Against Australia
